successes.title: California Headphones - Premium Metal & Leather Design
successes.description: Tired of Plastic headphones? California Headphones are retro designed die cast headphones wrapped in leather that sound insane

Pledges.description: ADD YOUR TRACK  - Show your support by adding your favorite track that you think would be perfect for the California Headphones sound and vibe! We'll list your name, the song, and your picture on the website. Original music only please. You must be the copyright owner of the song and picture you submit.
